{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"df3ea5145d","title":"对李克农等关于厚房管理工作请示的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c364049b7","index":0,"year":1953,"month":1,"day":21,"articleId":"df3ea5145d"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"f86748f621","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"df3ea5145d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李克农，当时任中央人民政府外交部副部长、中国人民解放军副总参谋长、朝鲜停战谈判中国人民志愿军代表团党委书记。"},{"id":"0af96c639c","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"df3ea5145d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指李克农、甘泗淇（军委总政治部副主任）、黄远（军委总政治部敌军工作部部长）1953年1月16日关于厚房管理处工作的几个问题给周思来、彭德怀的请示报告。这些问题包括：停管处的领导关系问题，特殊停房的处置问题，管处的驻地问题，外文干部问题，以及运输工具、教育工具问题。"}],"contents":[{"id":"79d92e4de0","type":"title","text":"对李克农\"等关于厚房管理工作请示的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"df3ea5145d"},{"id":"f86748f621","type":"paragraph","text":"管理仔房工作甚为重要，必须加派干部和兵力，并准备对故空降作战，一个也不能让故人动走。如果被动走了这批伴房，我们就没有本钱和敌做交换房的谈判了。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"df3ea5145d"},{"id":"0af96c639c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"df3ea5145d"},{"id":"97d8ee4b27","type":"paragraph","text":"一月廿一日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"df3ea5145d"}],"page":{"id":"4672e97277","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"df3ea5145d","start":453,"end":453}}}},"__N_SSG":true}